<div class="col five-sm clear">
<h2 id="section-top">Overview</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContentacdc1244c7954f2a9c940b64cc7eeb0b">
<div class="profile-pic">
<img alt="Claremont Private Hospital" border="0" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_column1Content_column1Content_SummaryAndPhotoModule_PhotoView_DisplayImage" src="/Services/UserControls/UploadHandlers/MediaServerHandler.ashx?id=27531"/>
</div>
</div>
<p>Part of Aspen Healthcare, Claremont Private Hospital provides Sheffield and South Yorkshire with the very highest standards of modern clinical care. Situated in beautifully landscaped gardens, patients enjoy a peaceful stay, consultant-led care and nursing excellence with a 60 year reputation. We have over 150 hospital staff, 280 expert NHS consultant experts, day-case suite, minor procedures suite, 3 operating theatres and a state of the art BUPA approved MRI unit.</p>
<p>We pride ourselves on excellent cleanliness and hygiene and have no known cases of hospital acquired infections such as MRSA. We offer an extensive range of inpatient and outpatient services.</p>
<p>Claremont Private Hospital is recognised by all health insurers and offers competitive fixed-price surgery for patients without health insurance.  We also offer some NHS services via Choose &amp; Book.</p></div>
</div>
</div>
